&lt;p&gt;Viant Technology (NASDAQ: DSP) is building the future of AI powered, identity driven advertising across CTV and the open internet. TVision plays a critical role in that ecosystem by delivering next generation audience measurement and attention insights that help advertisers better understand engagement, media effectiveness, and consumer viewing behavior. By combining connected devices, mobile technology, and advanced measurement capabilities, TVision powers the data and intelligence that help drive better media planning, optimization, and outcomes across the Viant ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Product Manager, you will own the end-to-end mobile experience for our panelists, as well as partner closely with the hardware and software teams that support our devices. You will work closely with Engineering, Panel Operations, Analytics, and Leadership teams to deliver reliable, scalable measurement solutions while balancing cost, performance, speed to market, and data quality.&lt;/p&gt;
