&lt;li&gt;Partner with technical leadership to define and execute the roadmap for devices, firmware, mobile applications, and OTA updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and monitor key success metrics including installation rates, device reliability, app engagement, data quality, and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate hardware and software release planning, ensuring dependencies are identified early and delivery remains aligned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage product backlogs, priorities, and agile processes while helping teams remove obstacles and maintain momentum.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create clear product requirements that translate panelist needs and business objectives into actionable engineering work.&lt;/li&gt;
