&lt;li&gt;Ability to navigate ambiguity and lead complex cross functional initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills with experience presenting to technical and business stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working with AI tools such as Claude, Gemini, ChatGPT&lt;/li&gt;
