&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;As a Sr. Technical Platform Operations Specialist, you will serve as a key operational liaison, ensuring the seamless performance of Viant’s products, including our Demand Side Platform (DSP). You will play a pivotal role in bridging cross-functional internal teams—such as Operations, Product, and Engineering—with external stakeholders and third-party partners. Your core responsibility is to maintain operational continuity through clear communication, technical insight, and a strong sense of urgency when addressing problems, challenges, and opportunities.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;This role requires a proactive approach to identifying root causes, facilitating resolutions, and driving alignment across multiple teams. You will own day-to-day technical operations, lead troubleshooting efforts, and support campaign and platform stability. The ideal candidate thrives in fast-paced environments, is a clear communicator, and demonstrates task leadership by translating customer and business needs into actionable solutions.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;THE DAY-TO-DAY&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the connective point between internal teams (e.g., Ad Operations, Product, Engineering) and external partners, driving the resolution of technical issues and ensuring the reliability of the DSP platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute and manage publisher integrations and 3rd-party partner certifications to ensure compliance and system compatibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide second-level QA and platform support, ensuring escalated issues are thoroughly documented and addressed with urgency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive cross-functional projects that enhance platform stability, operational workflows, and campaign execution quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate technical findings into clear, actionable feedback for both technical and non-technical stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;GREAT TO HAVE&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in ad operations, technical account management, or a related role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with at least one ad-serving or programmatic advertising platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills with a knack for documenting complex systems and workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to adopt and navigate new technologies quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of HTML/JavaScript&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
